flowchart TD
  START([send / schedule]) --> CREATE[create notification\nresolve template · compute checksum]
  CREATE --> DEDUP{dedup key active?\nnon-terminal exists?}
  DEDUP -->|yes| DUP[return existing\nrecord duplicate]
  DEDUP -->|no| PERSIST[persist · NotificationCreated]

  PERSIST --> MODE{send or schedule?}
  MODE -->|schedule| SCH[status = scheduled\nNotificationScheduled]
  SCH --> WAIT[(await tick when due)]
  MODE -->|send| DUE
  WAIT -->|due| DUE[deliver now]

  DUE --> EXP{expired?}
  EXP -->|yes| EXPIRED[status = expired\nNotificationFailed reason=expired]
  EXP -->|no| CH{channel registered?}
  CH -->|no| CHFAIL[status = failed\nChannelError reason]
  CH -->|yes| ATTEMPT[record attempt\nstatus = sent · NotificationSent]

  ATTEMPT --> DELIVER[provider.deliver model\nmeasure latency]
  DELIVER --> OK{ok?}
  OK -->|yes| DELIVERED[status = delivered\nrecord delivery · NotificationDelivered]
  OK -->|no / throw| RETRY{retryPolicy.shouldRetry?}
  RETRY -->|yes| RESCH[status = scheduled\nnextAttemptAt = now + backoff\nrecord retry · NotificationFailed willRetry=true]
  RETRY -->|no| FAILED[status = failed\nNotificationFailed willRetry=false]
  RESCH --> WAIT

  DELIVERED --> END([terminal])
  FAILED --> END
  EXPIRED --> END
  CHFAIL --> END
  DUP --> END
